I suppose we could lose one or two of the tea ladies.

78
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,960
别闹了 汉弗莱
Oh, Humphrey,

79
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:37,080
我确实希望你能端正下态度
I do wish you'd take this seriously.

80
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:39,720
端茶小姐 我要的是事实
Tea ladies I want the facts.

81
