为什么要压制消息?
Why does it suppress news?

100
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:27,120
因为他做得到的话 那别人也不得不节约了
Because if he can save money,everyone else will have to do it.

101
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,360
你何不调查一下
Why don't you look into it,

102
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:33,400
做个雪貂 四处打探(ferret:雪貂/打探)
have a bit of a ferret around?

103
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,520
你觉得我可以吗?
Do you think I could?

104
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,560
我觉得主意不错
I think that's a very good idea,

105
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,600
雪貂 哦不对 威瑟…埃瑟尔先生
Mr. Ferret erWeasel.     Hey

106
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,560
他告诉你是三千二百万英镑?
He told you 32 million pounds?

107
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,000
是的 汉弗莱爵士     我太震惊了
Yes, Sir Humphrey.     I'm aghast

108
