00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:18,120
你的那辆公家司机开的车呢?
What happen to the chauffeur driven car?

360
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:18,960
削减掉了
Got rid of it.

361
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:19,880
为什么?
Why?

362
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,200
连司机一起退掉了
Got rid of all the chauffeur, too.

363
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,760
所有豪华的办公家具
and all that grand office furniture,

364
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:25,720
藏酒 我私人办公室的大半人员
drinks cabinet, half the staff in my private office.

365
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:30,640
你被开除了     没有 没有
You've been sacked.     No, no...

366
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:34,160
那是为什么?     这叫节约运动
Then why?     It's an economy drive.

367
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,680
我在作表率
I'm setting an example.

368
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:38,720
没有奢侈品 没有虚架子 没有特权
No luxuries, no frills, no privileges...

369
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,240
你疯了
You're mad...

370
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:44,320
你做了20年后座议员 一直抱怨缺东少西
For 20 years you've complained you had no facilities.

371
