00:15:58,200 --> 00:16:00,720
说的不错 亲爱的 你以后当上首相
Yeah, darling. And how are you going to travel

377
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,120
打算以什么代步?
when you are Prime Minister.

378
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,280
搭便车?
Hitch hike?

379
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,680
伯纳德 来帮我整理日志
Bernard coming here for a diary cession…

380
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:15,160
好的 大臣 我把这一打好就来
Yeh, Minister. As soon as I've done this typing.

381
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,960
你不能让…
Can't you get…

382
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:18,720
真的不行 相当紧急
Not really, it's rather urgent.

383
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:20,760
裁员后 这儿就剩我们两个了
And since the cutbacks there's just the two of us.

384
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:21,920
我不得不打理一切
I have to do everything.

385
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,800
好吧 来我办公室 我必须和你谈谈
Well, come to my office I must talk to you.

386
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:25,840
曼迪 曼迪     什么事?
Mandy Mandy     Yes?

387
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,000
W键在哪儿?
Where's W?

388
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:29,280
左上角
Top left.

389
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,440
伯纳德 进来
Bernard Come in here

390
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,120
马上
Now

391
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:39,080
伯纳德 我们得重新安排我的日程
Bernard, we got to get these to my appointment.

392
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:41,720
我被预约了两处露面 而且已经迟到了一个半小时
I was double booked and is half an hours' late for that thing.

393
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,480
是什么 大臣?
What thing is?

394
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:44,320
商业效率展销会
The Business Efficiency Exhibition

395
00:16:46,040 --> 00:16:47,760
恕我直言 大臣 但基于…
I do apologise, but what with the...

396
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:50,280
您私人办公的裁员状况
staff economies in your private office,

397
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:51,880
搞清所有安排十分困难
it is awfully difficult to keep track.

398
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:53,960
这我也无能为力 下午的日程是
I can't help that. What's happening in the afternoon?

399
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,720
我这就去拿日志 大臣
I'll get the diary, minister.

400
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,520
现在不行 亲爱的
Not now, dear

401
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:03,080
现在不行
Not now

402
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,040
早上好
Morning

403
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,680
你非得现在打扫吗?
Do you have to do that now?

404
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:14,880
是的 他们裁掉了夜班工人
Yes. Yes. They've cancelled the night shift.

405
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:18,680
一些白痴又来什么节约运动了
Some idiot's started another of those economy drives.

406
00:17:20,560 --> 00:17:22,840
我叫妮莉     好的 重要的是...
I'm Nellie.     Good. Well, the point is...

407
00:17:22,840 --> 00:17:23,880
你是谁?
Who are you?

408
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,120
我是大臣
I'm the Minister.

409
00:17:27,320 --> 00:17:29,320
哦 真的?
Oh, really?

410
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:33,000
真的很高兴见到你
Oh, I'm ever so pleased to meet you.

411
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,400
我投了你的票
I voted for you.

412
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,440
好的 谢谢你
Oh, good. Thank you.

413
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:39,720
叫我妮莉就行
You can call me Nellie.

414
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,520
谢谢
Thank you.

415
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:43,640
我怎么称呼你?     吉姆
What do I call you?     Er... Jim.

416
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,600
这是日志 大臣阁下
Here's the diary, Minister.

417
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:48,520
好的 可以关掉它吗 亲爱的?
Right. Turn that off, would you, dear?

418
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:51,040
关掉 妮莉
Turn it... Nellie

419
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,520
什么?
What?

420
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:54,680
能让我们单独谈谈吗 这是机密
Would you excuse us? This is confidential.

421
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:57,520
你知道我得工作 吉姆
I've got to get on you know, Jim.

422
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:59,320
我也一样
So have I.

423
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:01,960
吉姆?
Jim?

424
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:04,840
好吧 我不用吸尘器
Well, I won't use the hoover.

425
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:07,160
我会踮起脚尖 你决不会留意到我
I'll tiptoe, you'll never notice me.

426
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:09,840
请出去     我轻如羽毛
Go please.     I'm light as a feather.

427
00:18:09,840 --> 00:18:11,600
出去 马上
Go Now

428
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:17,920
好吧 吉姆
All right, Jim.

429
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,320
我能领会
I can take a hint.

430
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:27,080
今天早上只有一位布拉夫先生 大臣
It's just a Mr.Brough this morning Minister.

431
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:29,960
我们东北地区的人力计划署主管
our Director of Manpower Planning to the northeast region.

432
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:32,640
布拉夫?     是的 裁员的事
Brough?     Yes, staff reductions.

433
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:34,200
哦 对    然后直接去上议院
Oh, yes.     And then straight to the House.

434
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:36,320
参加7点的质询 答复议员提问
