00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:39,600
8点钟要去法国总理大使馆参加招待会
at 8 o'clock the France prime minister reception at his Embassy.

436
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:40,120
好的
Right.

437
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:42,160
恕我失陪了 大臣
Would you excuse me. Minister

438
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:44,160
我得把日程送到组织秘书办公室去
I must take the schedules down to the Whips Office.

439
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,960
伯纳     大臣 什么事?
Bernard Bernard...     Yes, Minister?

440
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:50,200
值得一干 你知道
It is worth it, you know...

441
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:53,120
正中跨版 三张图片
Centre page spread and three pictures.

442
00:18:53,120 --> 00:18:54,720
是的 我读过了 大臣阁下
Yes, I have read it, Minister.

443
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,280
看我的图片
See this one of me,

444
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:59,760
拿着纸盒吃干酪卷
with a cheese roll on a cardboard plate?

445
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:04,120
"哈克的节俭体制下没有奢侈的午餐"
"No luxury lunches in Hacker's new austerity regime".

446
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:07,320
吉姆・哈克今天宣布"节约运动从'我'做起"
"Economy begins at home" said Jim Hacker today,

447
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:09,920
他为英国那群头戴圆礼帽
as he set an example to Britain's pampered army

448
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,800
娇生惯养的官僚树立了一个典范
