00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:13,080
太棒了 对吗?
Terrific, isn't it?

450
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,840
您已经给我读过了 大臣
You have read it to me already.

451
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:17,920
棒极了 对吗?     是的 大臣
Great, isn't it?    Yes, Minister.

452
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:22,880
节约正在起步(on the beach还有搁浅之意)
Economise on the beaches...

453
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:26,000
打扰了    什么事?
Excuse me.     Yes? Yes?

454
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,960
我想见大臣
I would like to see the minister.

455
00:19:28,320 --> 00:19:29,240
您预约了吗?
Do you have an appointment?

