00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,720
我叫罗恩・沃森 我是公务员系统
My name is Ron Watson, I'm the General Secretary

457
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:34,760
交通工人工会的总书记
of the Union of Civil Service Transport Workers.

458
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:35,880
好的 沃森先生
Yes, Mr. Watson.

459
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,600
听闻裁员将涉及到我们的会员
We're disturbed about rumours

460
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:39,760
我们倍感不安
of redundancies affecting our members...

461
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:41,560
抱歉 沃森先生 您不能见大臣
I'm sorry,Mr. Watson. you can't see the minister.

462
00:19:41,560 --> 00:19:42,680
您必须事先预约
You must have an appointment.

