00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:44,160
这样吧 明天打电话给我
Phone me tomorrow.

464
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,800
为何不能现在安排?
Why can't I arrange it now?

465
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:47,320
很抱歉     竟然这样
I'm sorry.     Oh, really

466
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:49,840
好吧 曼迪 安排沃森先生
Mandy, make an appointment for Mr. Watson

467
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:50,840
下周与大臣会面
to see the ministerfor next week.

