不是 布拉夫先生不得不取消会见
No. Mr. Brough's had to cancel the meeting.

486
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:37,440
我是罗恩・沃森 我来...
My name's Ron Watson. I'm...

487
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,400
很高兴您能替他来
I'm glad you could get here instead.

488
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:41,600
请坐吧 好吗     谢谢
Do sit down, won't you.     Oh, thank you.

489
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:43,280
好吧 恩...
Now, Mr. Er...

490
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:44,800
沃森
Watson.

491
