00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,280
我必须首先强调一点
there's one thing I must make absolutely clear.

493
00:20:49,280 --> 00:20:51,320
这话一定不能传出去
This must not get out.

494
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:53,840
要是工会听闻了风声
If the unions were to get to hear of this

495
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:57,640
准要闹翻天了
all hell would be let loose.

496
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,040
好的
Oh, yes.

497
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:02,680
当然要进行裁员 不裁减...
Of course there'll be redundancies. You simply...

498
