like this without getting rid of people.

500
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:11,320
最终 会裁减大量人员
Ultimately, a lot of people.

501
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:14,360
您为何不首先与工会商量呢?
Won't you be holding discussions with the Unions first?

502
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:16,760
我们会做做样子 进行磋商
We'll go through the charade of discussions,

503
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:18,760
但你也知道工会分子们都是些什么人
but you know what Trade Unionists are like;

504
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:20,760
就会胡搅蛮缠 个个愚蠢透顶
thick as two short planks and bloody minded.

505
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,280
个个如此?
All of them?

506
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:27,000
几乎都是 天哪 你该有体会
Pretty well. Good lord, you should know.

507
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:29,400
工会之间只热衷于互挖墙脚
They're interested in poaching each other's members

508
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:32,400
争上电视 还管不住自己的大嘴巴
and they can't keep their big mouths shut.

509
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:36,720
司机和交通服务人员怎么办?
What about drivers and transport service staff?

510
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:38,520
当然是首当其冲
First to go. Good lord.

511
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:40,720
我们在轿车与司机上浪费了大量财力
We waste a fortuna on cars and drivers.

512
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:43,720
而他们个个好逸恶劳     懂了
And they're all on the fiddle.     Oh, I see.

513
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,800
其实 我刚才正要解释
Because, as I was trying to explain that,

514
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:49,160
我不是布拉夫先生的代表
I'm not Mr. Brough's deputy.

515
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:52,360
我是公务员系统交通工人
I'm the General Secretary of the Union of

516
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:56,240
