00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:02,880
裁减我成员的谣传是否属实
the rumours of redundancies for my members.

520
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:06,840
好吧 我...
Well... I... I...

521
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:09,240
我刚才的意思是...
All I meant was...

522
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,320
哦 天哪
Oh, God.

